BUTTONS
=======

1) LABEL: "Draw Points"

2) LABEL: "Draw Line"

3) LABEL: "Draw Filled Circle"

4) LABEL: "Close Window" (if selected, "Open Window")


FIELDS CONNECTED TO EACH BUTTON
====================================

1) DIV: x coord (slider), y coord(slider), color picker
 add new

2)


- array of 4 buttons
	1st - Draw points with specified color
	2nd - Draw a line with specified end-points and color
	3rd - Draw a filled circle with specified center, radius, color